### [Negative][Register] Invalid phone format
POST {{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Bad",
  "lastName": "Phone",
  "email": "bad.phone@example.com",
  "password": "{{TestPassword}}",
  "personType": "Mechanic",
  "phoneNumber": "12345",
  "specialization": "GasolineAndDiesel",
