### [Negative][Register] Non-mechanic person type
POST {{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Customer",
  "lastName": "ShouldFail",
  "email": "customer.should.fail@example.com",
  "password": "{{TestPassword}}",
  "personType": "Customer"
