### [Negative][Register] Invalid expertise list (duplicate item expected)
POST {{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Bad",
  "lastName": "Expertise",
  "email": "bad.expertise@example.com",
  "password": "{{TestPassword}}",
  "personType": "Mechanic",
  "specialization": "GasolineAndDiesel",
  "expertise": ["Engine", "engine"]
}

