### [Positive][Login] Email-only user login by email
POST {{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{MatrixEmailOnly}}",
  "password": "{{TestPassword}}"
}

###

### [Positive][Login] Email+phone user login by email (uppercase normalization)
POST {{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "MATRIX.PHONE.USER.20260403A@EXAMPLE.COM",
  "password": "{{TestPassword}}"
}

###

### [Positive][Login] Whitespace email login (trim + lowercase normalization)
POST {{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "   MATRIX.WHITESPACE.USER.20260403A@EXAMPLE.COM   ",
  "password": "{{TestPassword}}"
}

###

### [Negative][Login] Existing user wrong password
POST {{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
